      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you aren't a doctor but i'm literally in agony and can't call anyone right now. i just need to know if it's actually dangerous or if people do it sometimes. like, if i take a couple of 325mg aspirins now, is that gonna do anything for the inflammation or am i just asking for trouble? i really just need the pain to stop so i can rest.",
